bout it.\"},{\"match\":\"470\",\"thought\":\"470. Eleven points short. The platform sees what I see.\",\"duration\":5000},{\"match\":\"Below recent cutoffs\",\"thought\":\"Recent STEM draws: 481-491. I'm 11 points below the lowest.\",\"duration\":3000},{\"match\":\"Age\",\"thought\":\"99 out of 110. Losing points every birthday.\",\"duration\":3000},{\"match\":\"Language\",\"thought\":\"136 out of 184. English is maxed. The missing points? That's French.\",\"duration\":3000},{\"match\":\"Skill Transferability\",\"thought\":\"100 out of 100. Maxed. Nothing left to optimize.\",\"duration\":3000},{\"match\":\"Additional\",\"thought\":\"0 out of 815. No job offer, no PNP, no sibling. This is where it hurts.\",\"duration\":3000},{\"match\":\"Take a French language test\",\"thought\":\"There it is. The platform is telling me what Chris will tell me. French CLB 7 adds points. 470 plus French equals above every STEM draw in history. Monsieur Nwosu's class might save my life.\",\"duration\":5000},{\"match\":\"Find a Consultant\",\"thought\":\"Find a Consultant. Chris Daw. FSWP specialist. CICC verified. He's on the other side of this button.\",\"duration\":5000}]]}]}],\"startedAt\":\"2026-05-24T16:54:31.372Z\"}"